{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"Show Q1 revenue by region ● running · 12s\n      \n      \n        \n        \n          AGENT\n          0s10s20s30s\n        \n        \n        \n          requirements\n          \n            \n            ✓ done\n          \n        \n        \n          kpi_discovery\n          \n            \n            ✓ done\n          \n        \n        \n          data_mapping\n          \n            \n            ● running\n          \n        \n        \n          data_quality\n          \n            \n            ● parallel\n          \n        \n        \n          exec_summary\n          \n            waiting…\n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      Timeline / Gantt Lanes ⭐ Recommended\n      Each agent gets a horizontal lane. Time flows left to right. Parallel agents show bars side-by-side. Completed = solid colour, running = animated pulse, waiting = grey. Instantly see who's parallel, who's blocked.","choice":"gantt","id":null,"timestamp":1781697690150}
{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"Agent Collaboration Feed\n      \n        \n        \n          req\n          \n            requirements_agent\n            Extracted 3 goals: revenue by region, exec summary, QoQ trend\n          \n        \n        \n          kpi\n          \n            kpi_discovery_agent\n            Found 6 matching KPIs. Passing to data_mapping + data_quality in parallel.\n          \n        \n        \n          dm\n          \n            data_mapping_agent ● typing…\n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      Agent Chat Feed\n      Each agent posts messages as it works — like a group chat. See what each agent is doing, what it passed to the next one. \"Typing…\" indicator for active agents. Real team feel.","choice":"chat-bubbles","id":null,"timestamp":1781697701741}
